{{flavour|Shoots a stream of webbing at a creature, ensnaring the target in a spider web.}}

'''Ensnare''' is a monster-only spell that blasts a target with a glob of sticky webbing, trapping it in place as though it had just been caught in a [[throwing net]]. 

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|[[Arachne]] will get [[Greater Ensnare]] instead.}}
*In [[0.20]] only, webs from Ensnare were permanent.

